<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Signup Confirmed</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #0e2f52; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa; }
        .email-container { background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(9, 135, 201, 0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0987c9, #7ed956); color: white; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; }
        .header p { margin: 10px 0 0 0; opacity: 0.9; font-size: 16px; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .content p { color: #5a6c7d; margin: 0 0 20px 0; }
        .content p strong { color: #0e2f52; }
        .event-card { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; margin: 25px 0; border-left: 4px solid #0987c9; }
        .event-card h2 { margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #0e2f52; font-size: 20px; }
        .detail-row { display: flex; padding: 8px 0; }
        .detail-label { font-weight: 600; color: #5a6c7d; min-width: 100px; font-size: 14px; }
        .detail-value { color: #0e2f52; }
        .status-badge { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #fbbf24); color: white; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 15px; }
        .info-box { background: #e0f2fe; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .info-box p { margin: 0; color: #0369a1; font-size: 14px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 25px 30px; background: #f8f9fa; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
        .footer p { margin: 0; color: #5a6c7d; font-size: 14px; }
        .footer .brand { color: #0987c9; font-weight: 600; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Signup Received!</h1>
            <p>Thanks for signing up</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <strong><%= studentName %></strong>,</p>
            <p>Your signup for the following event has been received:</p>

            <div class="event-card">
                <h2><%= eventTitle %></h2>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Date</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= eventDate %></span>
                </div>
                <% if (eventLocation) { %>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Location</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= eventLocation %></span>
                </div>
                <% } %>
                <span class="status-badge">Pending Review</span>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <p>The organizer will review your signup and confirm your participation. You'll receive another email once your status is updated.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p><span class="brand">Volunteens</span> - Connecting young volunteers with opportunities</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
